body:
Allowing for the UI recording of `persistence tests` and the ability to keep screenshots from multiple emulator restarts.

More details in commit messages.

@TychoVrahe feel free to try this for your homescreen use-case

Fixes #2849, fixes #2734 and possibly #2657.

